data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath near the highschool.  Watch the football games from your front porch!  Remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Dining room has built in cabinets while featuring a parque wood floor.  Down stairs features a common area that could be a family room and storage area along with a bonus room with a walk in closet.  New composition roof in 2020.  Wood floors throughout the upstairs living and bedrooms.  Relax in the hot tub! Make your appointment to see this home today!
